### 6. Complete Entity Hierarchy in world Package

All 33 entity files follow the same pattern:

**Core Entities:**
- `WWorld` - World container (with WorldInfo publicData containing hexGridSize)
- `WEntity` - Entity instances in world (with Entity DTO and position)
- `WEntityModel` - Entity templates (with EntityModel DTO)
- `WItem` - Item definitions (with Item DTO)
- `WItemPosition` - Placed item positions (with ItemBlockRef DTO)
- `WChunk` - Chunk storage references
- `WBlockType` - Block type definitions (with BlockType DTO)
